thread.title: John Johnson
thread.title_full: Test Me DNA reviewed by John Johnson

author: John Johnson
title: John Johnson
text: I called and got a nice guy who told me he would send the information out that day and he did. With tracking information. the Swabbing was very easy and I put the contents back in the envelope they send you and dropped it in the Fed Ex envelope, sealed it and dropped it off at the fed ex shipping location close to my home. Also with a tracking number and Pre Paid. They said for my tests it would take about 8-10 days but in five days got the call and the email to confirm the results I was checking for. Fast Simple easy and easy to understand results! Of course this test is all based on the integrity of the people who handle the swabs at home. but overall a great experience.
